OL,3,CTens of thousands of pounds of illicit
OL,4,Ctobacco seized in Scottish Borders
OL,6,FTens of thousands of pounds of illicit
OL,7,Ftobacco products have been recovered
OL,8,Ffrom two retailers in the Scottish
OL,9,FBorders.
OL,11,FIn a joint operation between Scottish
OL,12,FBorders Council and Police Scotland,
OL,13,Fthey visited two premises in the
OL,14,FScottish Borders after receiving
OL,15,Fintelligence regarding illegal tobacco
OL,16,Fsales.
OL,18,FTwo specially trained sniffer dogs
OL,19,Fhelped uncover the large quantity of
OL,20,Ftobacco products worth around #25,000.
