OL,6,FThe council have said that they want
OL,7,Fto thank members of the public who
OL,8,Freported the retailers.
OL,10,FConstable Mark Froud, Galashiels
OL,11,FCommunity Police Officer stated: "We
OL,12,Fcontinue to work alongside our
OL,13,Fpartners in Trading Standards to
OL,14,Ftarget any premises suspected of
OL,15,Fsupplying illicit products across the
OL,16,FScottish Borders.
